{"tid":880974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哈勃太空望遠鏡故障 NASA 嘗試重新開機解決","createTime":"2018-10-29T05:53:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-29T08:18:19.000Z","uid":56533,"like":13,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"7600ef27f6f8801a2d70b7ef57798d3b2d248876","tid":880974,"uid":56533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:53:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/s125e012033_1-694x461.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2Fs125e012033_1-694x461.jpg&h=58d79af6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n不論是多精密的系統，都會有壞機的時候，不過如果需要維修的東西是在太空，則更加麻煩。早前 NASA 的哈勃太空望遠鏡的陀螺儀壞掉，為了解決問題，NASA 嘗試了採用重新開機的方式修正系統，不過實情並沒有如此簡單。<br />\n<br />\nNASA 表示，出現問題的陀螺儀已經是個後備零件，原來的陀螺儀已經壞掉一段時間。這個後備陀螺儀的讀數最近出現異常，需要進入「安全模式」限制其功能。後來在 10 月中的時候，NASA 就採用了工程人員最喜歡使用的「重新開機法」，希望系統可以自動修復。然而其實這個「重新開機法」也不只是把系統關閉再開啓那麼簡單，而是把整個望遠鏡旋轉，重設其位置以希望清除之前累積的誤差。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2018/10/218652main_STOCC_FS_img_lg-694x422.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.unwire.hk%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F10%2F218652main_STOCC_FS_img_lg-694x422.jpg&h=0ec67c55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於 NASA 最初公佈消息的時候只說了他們把望遠鏡重新開機，導致不少人以為他們只是遙距把系統熄掉再啟動，因此後來他們發出更詳細的報告，解釋其操作其實非常複雜。目前望遠鏡的讀數已經比之前改善不少，需要繼續觀察是否穩定下來。哈勃望遠鏡已經有相當久的歷史，不少零件早已失效，不過要取代它所費不菲，因此目前依然盡力延長其壽命，繼續進行太空探索。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2018/10/27/nasa-didnt-fix-hubble-telescope-by-just-turning-it-off/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2018%2F10%2F27%2Fnasa-didnt-fix-hubble-telescope-by-just-turning-it-off%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=qmI7%2FJfYZh2CmzOCciuMjAHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=66d4b3f7\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2018/10/27/nasa-didnt-fix-hubble-telescope-by-just-turning-it-off/fun-tech/</a>"},{"pid":"51a6017d95e260663206e6e369dc56e2d52bf3dd","tid":880974,"uid":94501,"like":47,"dislike":2,"score":45,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:54:40.000Z","msg":"下至香港蚊型公司IT狗 上至NASA工程師 都係靠重開開機解決問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f18b054de47aa2cb98aeb3b03ef40a97a848fcc7","tid":880974,"uid":109983,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:55:33.000Z","msg":"愛回家terry<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fab3eebfdda13adbf3791beb1aace252e814432c","tid":880974,"uid":19712,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:56:07.000Z","msg":"reboot 果然係高招高招高高招"},{"pid":"b35ee32a5c21b6def7bd7e5dc7d397dd1770a03a","tid":880974,"uid":21917,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:57:23.000Z","msg":"Reboot 真係係萬用招式黎"},{"pid":"f12b67e04e767c9a07aeae0370d3ee0c8c21c7d9","tid":880974,"uid":6752,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:57:41.000Z","msg":"1兆應該夠射多幾支上去?"},{"pid":"d6117ea9d42b1f7a89db1f8df8ef79f3406c0a63","tid":880974,"uid":49136,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"換mon換keyboard唔得咩？"},{"pid":"b449cb8f19e19281d0362b923da9d1c02b76fb6a","tid":880974,"uid":71058,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"quote":{"pid":"d6117ea9d42b1f7a89db1f8df8ef79f3406c0a63","tid":880974,"uid":49136,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T05:59:05.000Z","msg":"換mon換keyboard唔得咩？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:13:23.000Z","msg":"好好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4bfd3b2819f82151641044a0e7dd6df3ca262c8c","tid":880974,"uid":511,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-29T06:17:38.000Z","msg":"Have you tried turning it off and on again?"},{"pid":"dac626bf2f2ca3e60e72a53110394a1a0